"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-delicious-orie-has-tasted-defeat-but-is-eyeing-sweet-success-at-paris-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Ben Hart  Team GB heavyweight boxing hope Delicious Orie has a simple message for his doubters: judge me at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 144, \"end\": 152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Hart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2766110183946712e-18, \"text\": \"Ben Hart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Hart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Hart\"}, {\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9204410448634297, \"rank\": 0.08640089724769086, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie, 26, is a Commonwealth and European Games champion but a run of three consecutive defeats at the start of 2024 has led some to reconsider his Olympic medal prospects.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 293, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\", \"score\": 0.9999997653158337, \"rank\": 2.335609746645617e-07, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\", \"score\": 0.9965229880459444, \"rank\": 0.002786609223630916, \"text\": \"European Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moscow-born Orie is bidding to emulate his idol Anthony Joshua with super heavyweight gold this summer.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anthony Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Joshua\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joshua is 4-0 sincehis much-publicised double defeat to Oleksandr Usykand all eyes are now on Orie to see how he bounces back from tough times.\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"score\": 0.9999994169076553, \"rank\": 5.8309287539842e-07, \"text\": \"Joshua\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joshua\"}, {\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Yanukovych\", \"score\": 0.9999995157273851, \"rank\": 4.842729410321224e-07, \"text\": \"Oleksandr\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Yanukovych\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Yanukovych\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With the game that I am in, it's relatively common to lose,\\\" said Orie.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You get into some bouts and it's just not your day, or the judging does not go your way, or the opponent is really good at that time.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, it's all about picking up that experience.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had a similar experience of defeat last year before the European Games.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's something I am able to learn from.\\\"\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't in the plan to blot his amateur record at the start of a seismic year, but Orie is looking at the bigger picture and asks that people reserve judgment for after the Games.\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The key is being able to keep grounded,\\\" said Orie, who benefits from monthly vouchers from\\u00a0Aldi\\u00a0for his all-important food shop, an initiative that has supported 1,000 athletes in the past four years.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1509, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Win, lose, it does not really matter, it's about being able to perform when it really matters and give everything when it matters, and for me, that's the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These are blessings in disguise.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I come out of those losses thinking: 'huge lesson, what are we going to do differently in the next fight?'\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's important I learn from my mistakes behind the scenes before the whole world is watching.\\\"\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The discourse over a defeat can often be overblown to the extent that a boxer's stock can plummet overnight.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Orie takes a different view of the odd reverse and is preaching patience, even if some corners of boxing social media are less inclined to afford him that privilege.\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's very common [that people are quick to jump on a defeat] and it's something that now I am starting to accept,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You get football teams that lose all the time but they are still great football teams.\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Muhammad Ali has lost, and Mike Tyson has lost.\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2518, \"end\": 2530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.889686221530936e-20, \"text\": \"Muhammad Ali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\"}, {\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.512154627035191e-43, \"text\": \"Mike Tyson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think society teaches you that failure is a bad thing and that if you fail, that's it, that's the end of you.\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But really, it's the only way you are able to get better.\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In school if you fail, you can not do this, or you have to retake that.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just embrace it.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These little failures are the reason I have qualified for the Olympics and will be representing Great Britain.\\\"\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldi\\u00a0have been the Official Supermarket ofTeam GBsince 2015.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2942, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Already one of Team GB's longest-serving partners, this partnership has now been extended to 17 years until 2032, reaffirming\\u00a0Aldi's multi-million-pound investment in both Team GB and its athletes.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3018, \"end\": 3025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9204410448634297, \"rank\": 0.08640089724769086, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}, {\"begin\": 3175, \"end\": 3182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9204410448634297, \"rank\": 0.08640089724769086, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The omens are good for Orie in Paris - every British super heavyweight boxer that has competed at the Olympic Games has won a medal.\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3233, \"end\": 3238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999976657818, \"rank\": 2.3343106151876868e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3247, \"end\": 3254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9999999974320417, \"rank\": 2.5673167774690593e-09, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he has loftier ambitions and remains steadfast in his plan to win Olympic gold, turn professional immediately after and start the road to becoming world champion.\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am up against world-class operators who are very experienced,\\\" said Orie.\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest, it's not new to me.\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I started boxing at 18 and starting late, you feel like you are always chasing, you are always the underdog.\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not in unfamiliar territory, I know that it's going to be difficult and I am aware of that.\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People want to test you until you break - that's just sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 3886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldi\\u00a0are proud Official Partners of Team GB & ParalympicsGB, supporting all athletes through to Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3888, \"end\": 3892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}, {\"begin\": 3984, \"end\": 3994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4568364004110953e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 3997, \"to\": 4110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4158, \"entities\": []}]}"